title: Yakisoba chicken stir fry
ingredients: ['1/2 teaspoon sesame oil', '1 tablespoon vegetable oil', '2 tablespoons chilli paste', '2 cloves garlic, chopped', '4 skinless, boneless chicken breast fillets - cubed', '125ml soy sauce', '1 onion, sliced lengthways into eighths', '1/2 medium cabbage, coarsely chopped', '2 carrots, coarsely chopped', '250g soba noodles, cooked and drained']
